    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a reinforced rear subframe, overhauled VANOS system, and updated rod bearings to ensure peak performance. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with surgical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, and the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed for maximum lateral grip. Finished in a concours-ready exterior with zero oxidation, this is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning purist.",
