    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality vehicle that defines excellence. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from a new car; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no creasing, and the interior retains its fresh, factory scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, benefiting from a fully documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment suite to the precision-tuned climate control, operates perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been treated as a prized possession. Includes all original keys, owner's manuals, and a comprehensive service portfolio.",
