    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out without a single worry to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for a new home, this is the one. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's chat!",
