    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This chassis is structurally flawless, having undergone professional rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan components. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, sending power to a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Preventative rod bearing replacement has been documented, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is fully optimized. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for quintessential steering feedback. This is a mechanically superlative example for the discerning purist.",
